{"tid":368426,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與學生性愛影片曝光 羅馬尼亞主教辭職","createTime":"2017-08-21T14:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T14:50:16.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c16af3175cadeb86337d6785fdabd28b0e9f58b","tid":368426,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:06:21.000Z","msg":"2017-08-20 19:49<br />\n羅馬尼亞東正教一位主教因為性愛影片曝光而辭職，根據媒體報導，影片中他與一名17歲神學院男學生發生性關係。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，東部城市胡西（Husi）主教巴拉德紐（Corneliu Barladeanu）的性愛影片從7月中在網上流傳，已在羅馬尼亞引爆醜聞。羅馬尼亞85%人口是東正教徒。<br />\n<br />\n教會管理機構聖主教會（Holy Synod）17日和18日開會討論此事。<br />\n<br />\n兩天的討論後，聖主教會在聲明中說，巴拉德紐自稱無辜，但「為了教會的平靜和福祉」決定辭職。教會內部的懲戒程序原本將持續幾個月，恐將使「他的教區面臨長時間不確定性。」<br />\n<br />\n巴拉德紐在教會不再有正式職位，還是修道士，但不能舉行彌撒。<br />\n<br />\n西元2000年以前同性戀在羅馬尼亞是非法的，在歐洲聯盟和歐洲理事會強烈批評後，羅馬尼亞才將同性戀除罪化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6812/2653735?from=udn_ch1cate7225_pulldownmenu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6812%2F2653735%3Ffrom%3Dudn_ch1cate7225_pulldownmenu&d=T5GqAMoknpQKFzmuFUSIu5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=bc460ff1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6812/2653735?from=udn_ch1cate7225_pulldownmenu</a>"},{"pid":"20cda1408e59775c2bf698baba1c02da6004220b","tid":368426,"uid":24623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:07:17.000Z","msg":"有冇片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bce37f8c2616e4a8a23ed14d0728fae3019b495","tid":368426,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:07:34.000Z","msg":"片呢，又冇片呀"},{"pid":"ea06df5b3f19d60dcf2f70c0f63e37b0cbb0c5f5","tid":368426,"uid":65128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:09:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"537e227d365884d94f2b1ebd6ec0d11242ba2d92","tid":368426,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:10:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f368900fe711de9f9d